snippet.title: The Super Mario Bros. Super Literature Club! Trailer (DDLC mod, Download link in description)
snippet.description:
https://superliteratureclub.carrd.co/

Mario and friends have come to Dokiland in their quest to get the brothers back to the Mushroom Kingdom. Will they find a way home, or will they fall into another of King Koopa's dastardly schemes?
